---
title: Cheesy-Peas-y Mushroom Ravioli with Golden Panko-Parm Topping
description: Get ready for an unexpected but familiar flavour application with this mushroom ravioli dinner.  A riff on the classic Italian cacio e pepe, we've kept the cheese but traded the pepper for the sweet pop of green peas!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/raviolis-aux-champignons-avec-petits-pois-et-fromage-8b52d9ef.jpg
